The paper focuses on face-related tasks such as age, gender, race, and facial expression estimation, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method is based on Multi-Task Learning (MTL) and data distillation, which are both topics in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of different datasets and domains, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural networks (cs.NE).
